## Customization

**Change the number of emails fetched** — edit the prompt in `fetchAndTriageEmails()`:
```js
"fetch the 10 most recent unread emails"  // change 10 to any number
```

**Add a new category** — add an entry to the `CATEGORIES` object:
```js
const CATEGORIES = {
  // ...existing categories
  followup: { label: "Follow Up", color: "#10B981", bg: "#10B98112", icon: "🟢" },
};
```

---

## Deployment

You can deploy this to Netlify in a few steps:

```bash
npm run build
```

Then drag the `build/` folder into [netlify.com/drop](https://app.netlify.com/drop), or connect your GitHub repo for auto-deploys.

